{100}{}{Tribal Leader}
{200}{}{You see: Tribal Leader}
{210}{}{This old man seems to be the leader of this tribe. Despite his age, he seems to be in a very good shape. His looks are in contrast with the other villagers, revealing his origins are not tribal at all.}
